          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the broccoli is cooking, slice the <strong>red chilli<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</strong> </span>finely</p><p>Once the broccoli is tender, add the <strong>drained noodles</strong> to the pan</p><p>Give everything a good mix up and cook for 1-2 min further or until the noodles are coated in sauce – this is your <strong>soy broccoli stir-fry</strong></p><p>Tip: Add a splash of noodle water to the pan if it's looking a little dry!</p>",
